{
  "texts": [
    "In 3DoF experiences, Passive types were preferred, while in 6DoF, Explorative types were favoured.",
    "Both DoFs demonstrated the use of Explorative interaction.",
    "Finally, Education showed a strong preference for 6DoF and the most interactive experience types.",
    "Even in 3DoF, the use of Passive was minimal.",
    "Explorative Interaction was the most frequently used experience type in 6DoF."
  ]
}